'''Infantophilia''' or '''nepiophilia''' (From Greek ''nepon'', "infant" + ''-philia'') is the primary sexual attraction of adults to very small children (usually defined as 0&ndash;3 years old).  This should not to be confused with [[infantilism]] (autonepiophilia).

